    Class Description
    AbstractSynthesizeModule
    Base class for different modules provide net synthesis.
    AbstractSynthesizeModule.Options
    Instances of this class hold options that can be specified for synthesis.
    FindWords
    Find all words that can be generated by a Petri net from a given class.
    FindWordsModule
    Find all words that can be generated by a Petri net from a given class.
    LimitedUnfolding
    Calculate a limited unfolding of a transition system, as defined in definition 2.42 in "Petri Net Synthesis" by Badouel, Bernardinello and Darondeau.
    LimitedUnfolding.DFSState  
    LimitedUnfoldingModule
    Provide the limited unfolding as a module.
    MinimizePN
    Synthesize a minimal Petri Net from a transition system.
    PNProperties
    Properties that a (synthesized) Petri Net can/should satisfy.
    Region
    An abstract region of a LTS.
    Region.Builder
    Helper class for creating Region instances.
    RegionUtility
    Utility class for generating regions.
    SynthesizeModule
    Provide the net synthesis as a module.
    SynthesizeModule.ReturnTS  
    SynthesizePN
    Synthesize a Petri Net from a transition system.
    SynthesizePN.Builder
    Builder class for creating instances of SynthesizePN.
    SynthesizePN.EventStateSeparationProblems
    Iterable for iterating over all event/state separation problems of a transition system.
    SynthesizeUtils

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    MissingLocationException
    A MissingLocationException is thrown when some events in a LTS have a location and others do not.
    UnreachableException
    An UnreachableException is thrown when some calculations are done on a node which require this node to be reachable from some other (initial) state.
